sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant TransferApp
    participant Agent
    participant ServerAPI
    participant RiskEngine
    participant Dashboard

    User->>TransferApp: Sends File
    TransferApp->>Agent: Detect File
    Agent->>ServerAPI: POST Event
    ServerAPI->>RiskEngine: Analyze Risk
    RiskEngine-->>ServerAPI: Risk Score
    ServerAPI->>Dashboard: Update Graph
    Dashboard->>User: Display Alert